title: BROUSKO 139
description:
Perilipsi:

Nees ekselikseis sto Mprousko afou o Axilleas tha dei sto spitaki pou xei kryftei o Shfhs thn Melina xwris na ton parei eidhsh ekeinh. O Axilleas exei ginei eksw frenwn me thn idea  oti emeine h Melina oloklhrh nyxta me ton Shfh kai den tou to eipe. Apo ton Mhna h Melina mathainei oti o Axilleas emathe to psema ths kai ekeinh tromokrathmenh den tou leei thn alhtheia kai tou leei ena kainourgio psema opou mplekei kai thn Dafnh se auto to psema. O Axxileas parolo pou einai poly tsantismenos den to deixnei kai den ths apokalyptei oti ta kserei ola kai gyrnane sthn Kypro. O Nektarios niwthei poly megalh sygkinhsh otan blepei thn fwtografia me ton didymo aderfo tou pou exei xasei.Apisteuth xara niwthei h Dafnh me ton Marko otan niwsei gia prwth fora to mwro tous. O patera ths Alikhs flertarei thn Kwnstantina kai ekeinh apogohteumenh endidei. O Shfhs parolo pou ton ekliparei h Anastasia kai h korh tou na gyrisei spiti ekeinos den feugei apo to spitaki sto bouno. O Axilleas pisteuei oti h Melina tou leei psemata giati niwthei poly megalh agaph gia ton Shfh.O Axilleas telika endidei sto flert ths Aleksias xwris na kserei oti h Melina tha epistrepsei nwritera sto spiti tous.
